data.description: Wanting to buy down your interest rate?? The seller is offering $5,000 towards the buyer's rate buy down or closing cost!! Discover your ideal home in a superb location! Welcome to 688 Hilchot Drive, a masterpiece of low-maintenance living. Step inside this inviting townhome, where you'll be greeted by abundant natural light and soaring ceilings, creating a spacious, airy ambiance. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting sleek stainless steel appliances. Your primary bedroom, complete with an en suite bathroom and a large walk-in closet, is conveniently situated on the main level, offering both convenience and privacy. Upstairs, you'll find two more generously-sized bedrooms, a shared bathroom, and a large loft/flex space, perfect for your unique lifestyle needs.You can step outside onto the screened back porch and savor serene pond views.Nestled within close proximity to the continuously developed Cane Bay and Nexton communities, you'll have easy access to an array of amenities that cater to your every desire. Take advantage of the community's offerings, including a refreshing pool, indoor pickleball courts for active recreation, tranquil nature trails for leisurely strolls, and picturesque waterfront views for moments of tranquility.Say goodbye to the hassles of home maintenance, as your HOA dues cover weekly landscaping and pressure washing, allowing you to enjoy the lifestyle you deserve. Don't miss your chance to make this splendid townhome your own - schedule a viewing today and experience the epitome of convenient, comfortable living!"
